Silicone camp killer maggot head style bust #horror #mask #halloween #stillkicking

Available now Freddy vs Jason movie mold Spencer Stump young Jason made by the Bill Terezakis fx team.  This will include a resin cast ridged foam filled armature of the actor , with the silicone prosthetic the actor wore. The products used to produce this bust are high quality smooth on resins , foam and dragon skin silicone.  This is how the fx team would have had this waiting to apply on the actor before the scenes were filmed.  Painted by Steve Bellamy @thedevilslatex and Robyn McCallum @thegoblingalstudio Acquired  by @spifftv  This mold has been in storage for over 2 decades and has never been offered to collectors.  Signed and numbered copies available for a limited time.  Please dm for purchasing info. #horror #halloween #freddyvsjason #mask #collector
